lines: 1. Ruoth, ok akwayoi tindeweche mag kiny;Rita kuom richo duto tetinendeni;Dhoga kik opus wach moroMa ok long`o;In mond` ibed Jarit dhogatinendeni.
2. Adwaro tiyoni matekkachiel galam;Konya abed mang`won e wach,gi tim bende;Miya teko mar winjoi,atim chikno;Konya kik atim dwaronatinendeni.
3. To kata ngimana dirumkwauononi;Mondo yuda kapadorakuom singruokni;Mit kata ok akwayoiweche mag kiny,Rita, taya, imaka, Ruoth,tinendeni.
